---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import sectionBackground from "./../../assets/images/secondSection_image.jpg"
// import sectionLine from "./../../assets/images/section-line.svg"
import SectionLine from './../../components/SectionLine.astro'
---
<section id="secondSection" class="relative">
  
  <!-- Section line -->
  <SectionLine/>

  <!-- Column layout TEXT -->
  <div class="relative grid grid-cols-6 lg:grid-cols-12 px-5 mb-12">
    <!-- Content columnt -->
      <div class="col-start-1 col-span-6 lg:col-start-2 lg:col-span-9 mt-[5rem]">
        <!-- Content wrapper -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="relative gtflexamed tracking-tight text-[10vw] leading-[9.2rem] uppercase">Popularita<span class="lowercase absolute text-green-800 bachelorette text-[5vw] -left-[4.5rem] bottom-[4rem]">glampingu</span><span class="-z-10">roste</span></h2>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>



    <!-- Column layout -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-6 lg:grid-cols-12 px-5">
      <!-- Content column -->
      <div class="col-start-2 col-span-6 lg:col-start-5 lg:col-span-4">
        <!-- Content wrapper -->
        <div>
          <p class="mb-8">Glamping je populární. Poptávka po něm celosvětově roste. Za noc v glampingu hosté zaplatí od 2 do 7 tisíc korun.</p>
          <p>Glamping propojuje kempování s pohodlím domova. Provedení je různé. Často se využívají modulární tiny-housy, stany nebo posedy. Kreativitě se meze nekladou.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <!-- Image div -->

    <div class="relative flex w-full h-80 bg-cover bg-center lg:bg-center" style=`background-image: url(${sectionBackground.src})`>
      <span class="text-orange-900 uppercase absolute rotate-[90deg]">Investujte do vlastního glampingu</span>
    </div>
    



</section>







